msgid ""
"9 default image size presets (Thumbnail, Small, Medium, Large, Gallery, "
"Hero, Banner, Card, Avatar) are protected system presets. You cannot delete "
"them or change their names, but you can modify their dimensions and quality "
"settings. You can create additional custom presets as needed."
